{"TopicId":155389,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Not really a question, but since when was a collision box added to the monolith?","CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T03:38:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T03:38:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was flying plane earlier and tried to fly through the monolith. It exploded.\u00A0 According to the flight log, the parts crashed into the monolith. Which means, the monolith has a collision box. Since when was that a thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"2204happy","CreatedById":174040,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T03:50:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIIRC it was 1.1.3 when Squad enlarged the monoliths added a colision box too them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T04:51:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot quite. Munoliths have had colliders all along. All the rest of them got colliders in 1.2.0.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"2204happy","CreatedById":174040,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T05:42:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh. Whoops!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I still think I was right on when they where enlarged.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T06:19:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh. Wellll, I hate to quibble with you again, but they didn\u0027t exactly get enlarged. Most of them got accidentally buried halfway underground in prior versions. But\u00A0they were still full sized. In 1.1.3 the devs went and made sure they all got elevated back to ground level again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Reactordrone","CreatedById":110060,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T06:51:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222930259\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485065946\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh. Wellll, I hate to quibble with you again, but they didn\u0027t exactly get enlarged. Most of them got accidentally buried halfway underground in prior versions. But\u00A0they were still full sized. In 1.1.3 the devs went and made sure they all got elevated back to ground level again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, either the monoliths got bigger or the Kerbals got smaller \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022monolith%20resize_zpsitvvuwgp.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v499/swampmonster/Kerbal%20space%20program/monolith%20resize_zpsitvvuwgp.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T07:47:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222930274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485067868\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110060\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Reactordrone\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, Reactordrone said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, either the monoliths got bigger or the Kerbals got smaller \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK, now I\u0027m gonna have to go check. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sharpy","CreatedById":145504,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T11:25:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe monolith at KSC2 is still small. (since I\u0027m in process of reactivating the site using Extraplanetary Launchpads, I know \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I definitely remember driving through the large monolith near \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E in the last 1.1.x\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Magzimum","CreatedById":167187,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T13:14:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup. My record to get a Kerbal on top of it is 1 min 07 seconds (from the moment the physics engine kicked in after launch from the Runway). Tested already back in November 2016...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xnXcVmf.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xnXcVmf.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/27292-what-did-you-do-in-ksp-today/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2857550\u0026amp;embedComment=2857550\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}